            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Linux</h3>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 dark:bg-yellow-900 dark:text-yellow-300">
              开发中
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
          Linux 版本正在开发中，敬请期待
        </p>
        <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">即将推出</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Windows 详细安装步骤 -->
  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <h2>Windows 安装详细步骤</h2>
    
    <h3>📋 系统要求检查</h3>
    <div class="not-prose mb-6">
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 border border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-200">安装前请确认</h3>
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-300">
              <p>请确保您的系统满足最低要求，并关闭杀毒软件以避免安装过程中的误报。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3>📥 下载安装程序</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>访问 <a href="/download">官方下载页面</a></li>
      <li>选择 <strong>Windows 版本</strong></li>
      <li>点击 <strong>下载安装程序</strong> 按钮</li>
      <li>下载 <code>玩机管家-Setup.exe</code> 文件（约45MB）</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>🔧 运行安装程序</h3>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>启动安装</strong>：双击下载的 <code>玩机管家-Setup.exe</code> 文件</li>
      <li><strong>安全提示</strong>：如果出现Windows安全提示，点击 <strong>"更多信息"</strong> → <strong>"仍要运行"</strong></li>
      <li><strong>管理员权限</strong>：在用户账户控制(UAC)提示中点击 <strong>"是"</strong></li>
    </ol>

    <h3>⚙️ 安装向导</h3>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>欢迎页面</strong>：点击 <strong>"下一步"</strong></li>
      <li><strong>许可协议</strong>：阅读并接受许可协议，点击 <strong>"我接受"</strong></li>
      <li><strong>安装位置</strong>：
        <ul>
          <li>默认路径: <code>C:\Program Files\玩机管家\</code></li>
          <li>可点击 <strong>"浏览"</strong> 更改安装位置</li>
          <li>点击 <strong>"下一步"</strong></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><strong>组件选择</strong>：
        <ul>
          <li>✅ 核心程序（必需）</li>
          <li>✅ 桌面快捷方式</li>
          <li>✅ 开始菜单快捷方式</li>
          <li>⬜ USB驱动程序（推荐）</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <h3>🚀 首次启动配置</h3>
    <p>安装完成后，首次启动需要进行以下配置：</p>
    
    <h4>激活程序</h4>
    <ol>
      <li>启动玩机管家</li>
      <li>在激活界面输入您的许可证密钥</li>
      <li>点击 <strong>"激活"</strong> 按钮</li>
      <li>等待激活验证完成</li>
    </ol>

    <h4>初始设置</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>设备检测</strong>：启用USB调试检测和网络扫描</li>
      <li><strong>界面设置</strong>：选择主题和语言偏好</li>
      <li><strong>安全设置</strong>：配置访问密码和数据加密</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>✅ 验证安装</h3>
    <p>完成安装后，请进行以下验证：</p>
    <ul>
      <li>在开始菜单中找到 <strong>"玩机管家"</strong></li>
      <li>启动程序，确认界面正常显示</li>
      <li>检查版本信息：<strong>帮助</strong> → <strong>关于</strong></li>
      <li>确认版本号为 <strong>2.1.0</strong></li>
    </ul>

    <h3>❓ 常见安装问题</h3>
    <div class="not-prose">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <summary class="px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg">
            安装程序提示"已损坏"或"无法验证"
          </summary>
          <div class="px-4 pb-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <p><strong>解决方案</strong>：</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-2">
              <li>重新下载安装程序，确保下载完整</li>
              <li>暂时关闭杀毒软件和Windows Defender</li>
              <li>以管理员身份运行安装程序</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <summary class="px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg">
            安装后程序无法启动
          </summary>
          <div class="px-4 pb-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <p><strong>解决方案</strong>：</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-2">
              <li>检查系统是否满足最低要求</li>
              <li>以管理员身份运行程序</li>
              <li>重新安装 Microsoft Visual C++ 运行库</li>
              <li>检查Windows更新</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <summary class="px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg">
            USB驱动安装失败
          </summary>
          <div class="px-4 pb-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <p><strong>解决方案</strong>：</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-2">
              <li>手动安装驱动：设备管理器 → 更新驱动程序</li>
              <li>使用安装目录下的 drivers 文件夹</li>
              <li>重启电脑后重新尝试</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 下一步 -->
  <div class="not-prose mt-12">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-emerald-50 dark:from-green-900/20 dark:to-emerald-900/20 rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-700">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
        <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🎉</span>
        安装完成！下一步做什么？
      </h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/docs/getting-started" class="flex items-center p-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
          <span class="text-2xl mr-3">🚀</span>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">快速入门</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">5分钟学会基本操作</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/docs/user-guide/device-connection" class="flex items-center p-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
          <span class="text-2xl mr-3">🔌</span>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">连接设备</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">学习各种连接方式</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
